據2011年12月11日的報導指出，韋斯特答應與[[印第安納溜馬|印第安納溜馬]]的2年2,000萬美元的合約。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://espn.go.com/nba/story/_/id/7341777/free-agent-david-west-signs-indiana-pacers|title=David West, Pacers have 2-year deal|work=espn.go.com|publisher=[[ESPN|ESPN]]|date=2011-12-11|accessdate=2014-07-04|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140624121814/http://espn.go.com/nba/story/_/id/7341777/free-agent-david-west-signs-indiana-pacers|archivedate=2014-06-24|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |authorlink=李玟 |url=http://www.nownews.com/n/2011/12/14/447372 |title=NBA／前黃蜂球星David West　兩年兩千萬美元加盟溜馬 |work=nownews.com |publisher=今日傳媒 |date=2011-12-14 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140704054739/http://www.nownews.com/n/2011/12/14/447372 |archivedate=2014-07-04 |accessdate=2014-07-04 }}</ref>

韋斯特在2013年1月12日以14分、12籃板和10助攻的成績，達成生涯首次大三元。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.indystar.com/article/20130112/SPORTS04/130112029/David-West-s-triple-double-leads-Pacers-win-over-Charlotte|title=David West's triple-double leads Pacers to win over Charlotte|date=2013-01-13|work=indystar.com|publisher=|accessdate=2014-07-04|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130115124631/http://www.indystar.com/article/20130112/SPORTS04/130112029/David-West-s-triple-double-leads-Pacers-win-over-Charlotte|archivedate=2013-01-15|dead-url=no}}</ref>

